      <title>法国陷入政治动荡 股市下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/french-markets-slide-as-snap-election-risks-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙突然决定提前举行大选，这给了投资者另一个抛售法国证券的理由，导致法国股市暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/french-markets-slide-as-snap-election-risks-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 10:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
